but there was something odd about her.

21
00:02:50.295 --> 00:02:54.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yeah. You mean that scent
of a new guy in her life?

22
00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:56.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Although she denies it.

23
00:02:56.885 --> 00:02:58.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Has she found a job?

24
00:02:58.511 --> 00:02:59.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ouch!

25
00:02:59.512 --> 00:03:03.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
