to work in sales at a fancy shop.

27
00:03:07.186 --> 00:03:08.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But it’s been at least a month

28
00:03:08.771 --> 00:03:10.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
since she was fired
from her previous job, right?

29
00:03:10.732 --> 00:03:11.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
How’s she getting by?

30
00:03:12.025 --> 00:03:13.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
