temporary jobs to get by.

32
00:03:17.238 --> 00:03:20.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But it’s not like there are
that many temporary jobs.

33
00:03:20.199 --> 00:03:23.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmm… She’s registered at a temp agency

34
00:03:23.453 --> 00:03:25.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
specializing in demonstrators.

35
00:03:25.204 --> 00:03:26.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What exactly does a demonstrator do?

36
00:03:28.291 --> 00:03:33.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
