Please give it a try.

37
00:03:34.088 --> 00:03:35.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>This demonstrator takes part</i>

38
00:03:35.757 --> 00:03:38.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>in campaigns to promote food items</i>
<i>which are new to the market.</i>

39
00:03:38.426 --> 00:03:39.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>You’ll find them in the food section</i>
<i>of department stores,</i>

40
00:03:39.636 --> 00:03:42.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>preparing anything</i>
<i>from sausages to sliced fruits.</i>

41
00:03:42.889 --> 00:03:45.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>In other words, I’m a food salesgirl</i>
<i>offering food samples.</i>

42
00:03:45.600 --> 00:03:47.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I get called for a sales blitz</i>
<i>that lasts for two, three days.</i>

43
00:03:47.810 --> 00:03:51.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I get paid over ten thousand yen a day,</i>

44
00:03:51.856 --> 00:03:55.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
